headline: Cadence Unveils HiFi iQ DSP to Power Next-Gen Voice AI and Audio
summary: CDNS unveils sixth-gen Tensilica HiFi iQ DSP, doubling compute, boosting AI up to 8x and cutting energy use to power next-gen voice AI audio.
